<h1>Subscription Booking Received</h1>

<p>Hello,</p>

<p>A new booking has been created for a subscription from <strong><%= @customer.full_name %></strong>!</p>

<h2>Booking Details:</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Customer:</strong> <%= @customer.full_name %> (<%= @customer.email %>)</li>
  <li><strong>Service:</strong> <%= @service.name %></li>
  <% if @staff_member %>
    <li><strong>Staff Member:</strong> <%= @staff_member.name %></li>
  <% end %>
      <li><strong>Booking Date:</strong> <%= @booking.local_start_time.strftime('%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p') %></li>
  <li><strong>Subscription Frequency:</strong> <%= @customer_subscription.frequency %></li>
</ul>

<p>The booking has been created and is ready for confirmation.</p>

<p>
  <a href="<%= business_manager_bookings_url(subdomain: @business.subdomain) %>">View Bookings</a>
</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
BizBlasts Team</p> 